(22, 'United International Picture', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '02-636-2438', '', '02-636-2440', 'Suite 1109, 11th Floor., Abdulrahim Place\n990 Rama 4 Road, Silom Rd,\nBangrak, Bangkok. 10500', '', '', 'WHO WE ARE\r\nUnited International Pictures (UIP), formed in 1981, is jointly owned by its Partners, Paramount Pictures and Universal Pictures. Since its formation UIP has distributed over 1,000 films including more than 100 Academy Award&reg; winners under licence from its Partners across the world. UIP continues to bring many of the most exciting films made today to international cinema audiences. \r\n\r\nWHAT WE DO\r\nOutside North America, UIP distributes Paramount and Universal films to cinemas in numerous countries, with distribution offices in 17 countries and third party licensees in a further 44 (for a full list of UIP offices and licensees please see our Global Directory).\r\n\r\nUIP also holds non-theatrical rights in all markets outside North America (see Non-theatrical).\r\n\r\nNON-THEATRICAL\r\nNon-theatrical distribution enables audiences outside conventional cinemas to access our films. UIP distributes Paramount and Universal titles non-theatrically throughout the world outside North America. We also distribute on behalf of other licensors in certain markets.\r\n\r\nUIP licences titles for group screenings on video, DVD or Blu-ray to film clubs, schools, universities, coaches and many other institutions. UIP offers the latest films in digital formats for video on demand (VOD) and pay per view in-room entertainment for hotel guests and hospital patients. Titles are typically available three months after cinema release.\r\n\r\nIf you have further queries please contact: ntenquiries@uip.com\r\n\r\nWORKING FOR UIP\r\nLike all businesses, UIP owes its success to the quality and commitment of its people. UIP\'s offices are run by local industry experts that understand the nuances of their particular marketplace and are able to develop strong relationships with local media and exhibitors. Our commitment to staff training ensures we maintain the high levels of professionalism and customer service needed to succeed in an increasingly competitive marketplace.\r\n\r\nTo find out about current job opportunities at UIP, please contact our HR team: hr@uip.com\r\n\r\nUIP AND THE EU\r\nUIP has offices in several EU countries and has given certain undertakings to the European Commission. We are committed to pursuing these undertakings and take all our responsibilities thereunder very seriously.\r\n\r\nTo view UIP&rsquo;s undertakings to the European Commission, please see the following: EU Undertakings', '28', '41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-10-24 11:24:23', '77', '22', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.uip.com/', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
