(50, 'BBV Systems Co., Ltd.', 84, 38, NULL, 'info@bbv-systems.co.th', '035-387-290', '-', '035-387-295', '111/34-36,Fast Fact bLDG, Moo 2, Phaholyothin Rd, Lamsai, Wangnoi, Ayutthaya 13170', '', '-', 'BBV Systems Co., Ltd. (BBV Asia) was incorporated in the Kingdom of Thailand in 1999 and enjoys privileges from the Board of Investment (BOI) and is registered with the Ministry of Commerce. BBV Asia is a member of the internationally active Bilfinger Berger SE Group and its main stakeholder is BBV Systems GmbH (BBV), Germany. The web link as below :\r\n\r\nBilfinger Berger SE:www.bilfinger.com\r\nBilfinger Berger Civil:www.civil.bilfinger.com\r\nBBV Systems GmbH:www.bbv-systems.com\r\n\r\nThe company&rsquo;s core competence lies in its ability to develop and produce low to high grade threaded steel bars and related accessories (BB BAR, BAREX and TEREX&reg;) with a focus on post-tensioning, geotechnical, mining and concrete reinforcing systems.\r\n\r\nOur policy is to provide a strong customer orientated service supported by our ISO 9001:2008 quality assurance program starting with design and concept of our products, sourcing of raw materials and including manufacturing and rigorous testing with ongoing development and improvement of our product range.\r\n\r\nToday, BBV Systems has a well-established distribution and sales network in many countries throughout Asia, Australia the Middle East, Europe and Canada offering solutions for challenging tasks and simplifying difficult tasks is the specialty of BBV engineers. Dedicated to the corporate philosophy BBV Systems is maintaining and widening a reputation for high-quality products and workmanship at competitive costs.\r\n\r\nQualified supervisors and/or special equipment such as stressing jacks and pumps etc. can also be supplied for the installation of our systems.', '39', '30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2017-10-16 10:26:58', '128', '24', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.bbv-systems.co.th/', '0', '0', '1', 2, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
