(66, 'Essilor Manufacturing (Thailand)', 80, NULL, NULL, '', '02 326 0440-3', '', '02 739 4640', '213 Latkrabang Industrial Estate Zone 3 Chalongkrung Road \nLampatiew Latkrabang\nBangkok 10520', '', '', 'Essilor Manufacturing (Thailand) Co., Ltd. is part of the worldwide footprint of the France-based Essilor International Group, the world leader for corrective lenses. The plant was set up in 1990 in the free zone of Latkrabang Industrial Estate (Bangkok) and is the biggest plant in Essilor worldwide network.\r\n\r\nThe Essilor group defines Corporate Sustainability as the overall long-term performance of the company. In this framework, EMTC ensures EH&S compliance level through OHSAS 18001 and ISO14001 Certification showing the plant’s commitment for a safe and clean work environment, satisfied employees and security of industrial processes.', '24', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2016-06-15 11:06:13', '177', '16', '2014-01-15', 'www.essilor.com', '1', '30', '0', 100, '', NULL, '7', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(67, 'Bangkok Self Storage CoLtd', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info@bangkokselfstorage.com', '02 261 1516-7', '', '02 661 3538', '3249 Rama IV Road\r\nKlongtoey Bangkok 10110', '', '', 'Bangkok Self Storage specialises in delivering high quality, on-demand storage solutions for a busy and demanding clientele.\r\nWe develop and operate modern self storage facilities for personal, business and leisure storage.\r\n\r\nUnlike Asia where this concept of \'Do-It-Yourself&quot; storage is new, self storage is a very common form of storage known to those living in Australia, Canada, the United States and Europe. Bangkok Self Storage aims to bring this brand new way of storing to Thailand, providing a one stop storage solution for everyone and anyone who needs it.\r\n\r\nDespite Bangkok Self Storage&rsquo;s short existence, we have been growing from strength to strength, bringing world-class services at competitive prices to our customers. Serving both the corporate and consumer markets, Bangkok Self Storage is constantly challenging itself to develop innovative and useful features that meet all our customers\' needs.\r\n\r\nWe are a service-driven operator, who firmly believes that our business has a great future in this part of the world. Driven by the increased interest in and demand for self storage within Thailand, we are dedicated to providing Bangkok with a brand new way of storing.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Austcham 14/3/07 Director Mr.John Elliott Facility Manager Mr.Darrel Lintott&lt;/p&gt;', '16', '41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-10-24 15:47:19', '77', '16', '2014-01-15', 'www.bangkokselfstorage.com', '0', '2', '0', 2, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
