(79, 'Rhenus Prolog Logistic CoLtd', 84, NULL, NULL, 'recruitment@th.rhenus.com , malinee.nanakorn@th.rhenus.com', '02-261-5380', '', '02-261-5386', '191/14 CTI Tower 28th Floor\nRatchadapisek Rd., Klongtoey\n Bangkok 10110', '', '', 'Rhenus Logistics Co., Ltd. in Thailand has extensive experience in providing logistics solutions for a large variety of shipments, specialized in a number of fields such as electronic goods, semi-conductor and the automobile industry. Established in 1994, the company has been growing ever since, opening its airport office 1996 and being a full spectrum service provider for air, sea, domestic transportation and customs brokerage by 1997. What started as a handful of people grew to an office boasting over 200 full-time employees distributed over four offices and five warehouses in the country.\r\n\r\nThailand is a leading member of ASEAN and one of the fast-growing economies in South East Asia. In addition to Thailand&rsquo;s well developed semi-conductor and electronics industry, Thailand is also a leading automotive manufacturer and exporter, earning the nickname as the &ldquo;Detroit of the East&rdquo;. The main airport in Bangkok is a regional transportation hub with over 100 airlines flying on scheduled basis. Thailand&rsquo;s deep-sea port at Laem Chabang has direct access with the Eastern Seaboard Industrial Estates which are the manufacturing hubs for the country.\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;New Company Logistic&lt;/p&gt;', '18', '5', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-10-24 16:51:34', '77', '16', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.pro-logistics.com/index.php', '0', '3', '0', 3, '', NULL, '4', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
