(172, 'Takachiho Fire Security amp ServicesThailand', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'enquiries.th@tycoint.com', '02 366 9000', '', '02 366 9090', 'TCIF Tower, 25th Floor, \n1858/110-111 Bangna-Trad Road,\nBangna, Bangkok Thailand 10260', '', 'Takachiho Fire, Security &amp; Services (Thailand) Ltd.\r\n\r\n\r\nTel: 02 366 9000       \r\nFax: 02 366 9090', ' Takachiho Fire &amp; Security Services is one of the leading providers of security solutions to residential, business and governmental customers and is one of the largest fire protection companies in Thailand. Working across a wide range of industries and customers.\r\n\r\nThe Company has once named \'Tyco Fire, Security and Services (Thailand) Ltd.\' but after changing hand from Tyco International to Takachiho Koheki in mid 2011,  we becomes the distributor of Tyco International for Thailand area. And now we are ready to help you identify and reduce areas of risk for your business and offer solutions to help protect your employees, your assets, and yourself\r\n\r\n Our security solutions included:\r\n\r\nCCTV monitoring\r\nAccess Control\r\nVideo Surveillance\r\nRadio Frequency Identification (RFID)\r\nIntrusion Detection\r\nElectronic Article Surveillance (EAS)\r\nSource Tagging\r\nOur fire protection solutions included:\r\n\r\nFire protection systems\r\nGaseous Fire Suppression\r\nFire Detection\r\nSpecial Hazard\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;New Company American Chamber&lt;/p&gt;', '16', '7', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-10-31 11:59:18', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.tkfs.co.th/', '0', '1', '0', 1, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
