(297, 'Jusmag Thai ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'admin@jusmagthai.com', '02-287-1036', '', '02-286-9271', '7 Sathorn tai Road \nTungmahamek,Sathorn\nBangkok, 10120 Thailand', '', '', 'USMAGTHAI is the U.S. Security Cooperation Office (SCO) in Thailand. The Chief of JUSMAGTHAI is also the Senior Defense Official (SDO). In addition to its military chain of command at United States Pacific Command (USPACOM) in Hawaii, JUSMAGTHAI is also directly responsible to the U.S. Ambassador to Thailand. Unlike most SCOs, JUSMAGTHAI has primary responsibility, or otherwise directly supports, a wide variety of missions. These include a robust Joint & Combined Exercise Program (averaging over 85 exercises per year training over 10,000 US service-members), International Military Education and Training (IMET), Foreign Military Sales, Humanitarian De-mining, and Military Medicine exchanges.', '32', '4', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2016-06-06 14:51:34', '177', '2', '2014-01-15', '', '0', '5', '0', 5, '', NULL, '2', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
