(375, 'Factorytalk Co Ltd', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'contact@factory-talk.com', '+66 2 630 4525  ', '', '+66 2 630 4527', '12th Floor, Liberty Square\n287 Silom Road, Silom, \nBangrak, Bangkok 10500,', '', '', 'Factorytalk: Expertise across the regulated industries\r\n\r\nFactorytalk established in 2004 and with locations across South East Asia provides specialist Compliance Services and Technology Solutions to the regulated industries. We are highly active within Asia and from our headquarters in Thailand and from our regional branch offices we work tirelessly and globally on mission critical assignments for our clients.\r\nWe are experienced in helping firms establish efficient, cost effective quality systems that will pass inspection and produce high quality products. Our consultants review business processes and methods to make them more efficient, to follow best practices and robust enough to stand up to current regulatory challenges.\r\nOur solutions experts help our customers develop strategies and processes that work by integrating timeless manufacturing principles with 21st century technology to produce astonishing results.\r\nWe provide dedicated project and off-shoring teams to our clients to leverage our industry knowledge and experience with our principles to deliver on time, within budget whilst ensuring the highest international levels of quality and compliance.\r\nFor sales and marketing support we offer the leading vendors of sophisticated IT products &amp; services access to quickly and predictably acquire new customers, all without the humiliation of competing only on the basis of price.\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;German Cham 16/3/07 Technical Director: Mr.David Margetts&lt;/p&gt;', '60', '8', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-02 14:41:05', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.factory-talk.com/', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(376, 'Webster University Thailand', 231, NULL, NULL, '', '02-652-0705-7', '', '02-652-0708', 'Maneeya Center (E1), 10th Floor\r\n518/5, Ploenchit Road, \r\nBangkok 10330, Thailand\r\n\r\n', '', '', 'n American University where the World is Your Campus\r\nAt Webster University, the education is American and your campus is the world. While studying at the Webster University Thailand Campus, you will benefit from the University&rsquo;s global network of campuses and the international perspectives of its academic programs.\r\n\r\nWebster has been recognized as a leader in American education for more than 30 years. Founded in St. Louis, Missouri, U.S.A. in 1915, Webster University is consistently rated as a top tiered college in ranking of universities in USA News &amp; World Report and Forbes Magazine. Webster University has a global network of over 100 campuses including the Thailand Campus, which is one of the most popular international campuses of the Webster University system.\r\n\r\nStudy in Amazing Thailand\r\nAsia is growing and you get to be in the center of it when you study in Thailand. Webster University Thailand is a small, closely-knit family of students, faculty and staff occupying a delightful rural campus, situated close to the resort towns of Cha-am and Hua Hin.\r\n\r\nIt is located approximately 185 Kilometers south of Bangkok. At the Cha-am campus, mainly undergraduates follow their chosen degree programs, while graduate students occupy outstanding facilities at the Bangkok Centre, which is within walking distance of the major shopping facilities around Siam Square in the enchanting city of Bangkok.\r\n\r\nAt present WUT has a student population of around 500 students with a recruiting initiative currently underway to reach a target of 1000-1200 students.', '49', '1', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-02 14:58:01', '77', '16', '2014-01-15', 'www.webster.ac.th', '0', '13', '1', 13, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
