(423, 'Grasso (Thailand) Co., Ltd.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info.grasso.th@gea.com', '02 525 8500', '', '02 525 8555', '93/20, Soi Lat Phrao 87Lat Phrao Road\nWang Thonglang\nKhet Wang Thonglang\nBangkok, 10310', 'GEA Refrigeration Netherlands N.V.,\r\nTechnology Center Piston Compressors &ndash; GEA Grasso\r\nParallelweg 27\r\nP.O. Box 343\r\n5201 AH \'s-Hertogenbosch\r\nThe Netherlands\r\nP: +31 (0)73 6203 911\r\nF: +31 (0)73 6214 320\r\ninfo@grasso.nl\r\n', '', 'It&rsquo;s long history and attention to quality gained Grasso the title of Royal Machinery Manufacturer - Grasso&rsquo;s Koninklijke Machinefabrieken. Since 1986, Grasso is the leading company of GEA Refrigeration, a division of the multinational GEA Group in Germany. \r\nWith time, GEA Refrigeration became one of the world&rsquo;s greatest industrial producers of piston and screw compressors, compressor aggregates and ammonia chillers. These units are currently manufactured in four plants in Holland, Germany and USA. Additionally, GEA Refrigeration includes many other producers producing different refrigeration equipment and installations.\r\nWhy our clients choose Grasso:\r\nThe extensive range of high quality, reliable and modern refrigeration compressors, can be applied in almost every industrial refrigeration process. The products have been designed, developed and built by people who know just how much can depend on attention to detail and are distributed worldwide to contractors, distributors and Original Equipment Manufacturers (OEM\'s).\r\nOur commitment to reliability does not end when your chosen product is installed and commissioned. To us, that just the start of what we trust will be a long and fruitful working relationship.\r\nWe provide you with truly optimal support backed up by our worldwide service network.This includes rapid response to requests for technical information and internet facilities that digitally support you in the decisions you make when putting together the most efficient refrigeration and air conditioning packages.\r\nWith the knowledge and experience of the whole Grasso Group we are able to satisfy the most refined demands of our customers and finalize the most unusual orders.', '60', '9', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2015-02-16 13:59:15', '153', '24', '2014-11-01', 'http://www.grasso.nl/en-us', '0', '3', '0', 3, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
