(634, 'Hunters Investments Limited', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info@venator.co.th ', ' + 66 (0) 2667 0033', '', '+ 66 (0) 2667 0034', 'Unit 101, 10th Floor, Sitthivorakit Building, \nSilom Soi 3, Silom,\nBangrak, Bangkok 10500', '', '	\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nContact us \r\n\r\n\r\n	\r\n', 'dvisory Services Offered\r\n	 Mergers and acquisitions (cross-border and domestic)\r\n	Divestments, spin-offs, buy-outs\r\n	 Joint venture planning and negotiation\r\n	 Business and financial restructuring\r\n	 Valuation and financial sensitivity modelling\r\n	Sourcing capital through private equity, mezzanine debt placements\r\n	Transaction project management and business due diligence management\r\n 	 \r\nWhere We Differentiate\r\n	Venator Advisory distinguishes itself by providing quality advisory services that are differentiated by our creativity, technical excellence and commitment of our firm\'s professionals.\r\n	Venator Advisory\'s professionals draw on many years of transaction experience to provide highly informed counsel in connection with transaction structuring, business due diligence, financing considerations and strategic-level decision making.\r\n	Venator Advisory provides balanced independent advice whilst maintaining a sharp focus on the business rationale that is of critical importance in any corporate undertaking.\r\n	Venator Advisory was established as a direct response to the growing need for professional independent financial advisory services in the Thai market at a time when investment banks and traditional financial houses are restricting their activities to larger scale transactions.\r\n	As in any industry, the success of transactions requires knowledge of the local market, the underlying operating entities and their activities, familiarity with prospective business and financial partners and the competitive environment, relationships with the business community, as well as an established in-depth understanding of the macroeconomic and social conditions. We are confident in the ability to weave these elements together in working hand in hand with our clients.\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Call and Send E-mail 13/2/07 Philip Visit and give Brochure 6/2/07&lt;/p&gt;', '7', '8', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-07 15:52:37', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.venator.co.th/service.htm', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
