(861, 'Halliburton Energy Services Inc', NULL, NULL, '', '', '02-278-8100, 02 278 8124', '', '02-278-8199, 074 302 257', 'Sun Tower  B Building Unit No.- 15th Fl. \r\n123 Soi - Vibhavadi-Rangsit Rd., Jompol, Chatuchak, Bangkok 10900 Thailand', '', '235/5 Moo 2 Lopburi-Ramate Road,\r\nTambol Phawong, Amphur Muang,\r\nSongkhla 90100, Thailand.', 'Corporate Profile\r\nFounded in 1919, Halliburton is one of the world&rsquo;s largest providers of products and services to the energy industry. With more than 75,000 employees, representing 140 nationalities in approximately 80 countries, the company serves the upstream oil and gas industry throughout the lifecycle of the reservoir &ndash; from locating hydrocarbons and managing geological data, to drilling and formation evaluation, well construction and completion, and optimizing production through the life of the field.\r\n\r\nOur Business\r\n\r\nHalliburton comprises 13 product service lines (PSLs). The PSLs operate in two divisions: Drilling and Evaluation, and Completion and Production. Our Consulting and Project Management PSL works across both divisions and is the spearhead of our integrated-services strategy. Its financial results are included in the Drilling and Evaluation Division. PSLs are primarily responsible and accountable for strategy, technology development, process development, people development and capital allocation.\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;K. Apaipan Hongsamart Human Resources Supervisor &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:apaipan.hongsamart@halliburton.com&quot;&gt;apaipan.hongsamart@halliburton.com&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;02 278 8147, 089 661 3847 &lt;br /&gt;Chanakan Theera-Anurukkul (Shirley) Halliburton Indo-China Tel: +662 278 8139 Fax: +662 278 8199 Email: &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:Chanakan.Theera-Anurukkul@Halliburton.com&quot;&gt;Chanakan.Theera-Anurukkul@Halliburton.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;235/5 Moo 2 Lopburi-Ramate Road, Tambol Phawong,Amphur Muang, Songkhla 90100 &lt;br /&gt;Thanaporn Tawee