(862, 'ColgatePalmolive Thailand Ltd', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '02 229 8000 ext. 4147, 02 229 8147', '', '02 249 3869', '19 Off Na-Ranong Rd., \nSunthornkosa Rd. Klongtoey\nBangkok 10110', '', '', 'Colgate-Palmolive (Thailand) manufactures and markets Colgate toothpaste, toothbrushes, mouthwash and dental floss; Palmolive, Protex, Care shower cream; Care and Protex talcum powder; Action hairdressing.\r\n\r\nIn 1806, when 23-year-old soapmaker William Colgate began operating his own business in Manhattan, New York, little did he know that he was to sow the seed of what was to become one of the largest corporations in the world.\r\n\r\nFrom its humble beginnings, the company has grown to employ more than 36,000 people at 95 plants and facilities. They produce more than 5,000 different products used by millions of consumers in 135 countries.\r\n\r\nThe company first entered the Thai market in 1958 and, in 1979, established its own distribution channels to enhance customer service. In 1995, it started a new National Distribution Center and manufacturing operations. It is owned by Colgate-Palmolive Company.\r\n \r\n&lt;p&gt;88888 K. Hiranya Chantapong hiranya_c@copal.com 081-812-3591 New managing director: Giriraj Bagri. 27.06.08 K.Mukul Deoras Managing Director (mukul_deoras@colpal.com) 23 October 2007 Perayaporn_Srisupap@colpal.com Secretary of K. Hiranya. Cookie and Book 20/12/06 K.Gerry Bautista (Hr.Director)(Gerry_Bautista@colpal.com) K.Wilawan - 08-9996-4387(K. Hiranya Asistance) (Wilawan_P@colpal.com) K. Vanee B(Vanee_B@colpal.com) Dorset Sutton Managing Director&lt;/p&gt;', '43', '41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2015-03-09 14:44:21', '153', '24', '2014-01-15', 'www.colgate.com', '0', '0', '1', 0, '', NULL, '18', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
