(871, 'POSCO-Thainox Public Company Limited', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'career@poscothainox.com', '+66 (0) 2250 7622-32 ', '', '+66 (0) 2250 7633', '15th Floor, 622 Emporium Tower\r\nSukhumvit 24, Klongtan, Klongtoey, Bangkok 10110', '', 'POSCO-Thainox Rayong Plant\r\n324 Moo 8, Highway no. 3191 Road, \r\nTambol Mabkha, Nikom Pattana, \r\nRayong 21180 THAILAND\r\nTel: +66 (038) 636 125-32\r\nFax: +66 (038) 636 099', 'POSCO-Thainox: A Synonym of Quality\r\n&lsquo;POSCO-Thainox&rsquo; stainless steel products and production strictly adhere to the industry&rsquo;s major international standards &ndash; AISI (American Iron and Steel Institute), ASTM (American Society for Testing and Materials), JIS (Japanese Industrial Standards), EN (Euro-Norm Standards), ISO (International Organization for Standardization) and TIS (Thai Industrial Standard) &ndash; thus, being recognized and highly regarded in more than 40 countries worldwide.\r\nIn addition to offering a wide variety of stainless steel grades, POSCO-Thainox also produces stainless steel according to the individual customer&rsquo;s orders and specifications. Each order is always handled with particular care by our professional staff belonging to the Commercial, the Production Planning, and the Customer Technical Service &amp; Development teams, who altogether work in close collaboration to provide the best suitable steel catering to every customer&rsquo;s wants and needs.\r\n\r\nDuly certified according to ISO 9001 standard, POSCO-Thainox&rsquo;s rigorous quality control is maintained in every step of the production process &ndash; from metal requirements to cold-rolling, finishing, and shipping to customers &ndash; through a reliable, state-of-the-art computerized system. This enables us to provide a personalized service and short delivery lead-times. \r\n', '2', '5', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2018-02-05 10:14:03', '128', '24', '2018-03-01', 'www.poscothainox.com ', '0', '0', '0', 8, '', '', '0', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0