(883, 'Pacific 2000 International Recruitment Co Ltd', 0, NULL, NULL, 'mayureep@pacific2000.com', '02-654-0300', '', '02-654-0299', '8th Fl., M Thai Tower, All Seasons Place\n87 Wireless Rd., Patumwan\nBangkok 10330', '', '6th Floor, Bangkok Bank Building\r\nPacific Park\r\n98 Sukhumvit Road Siracha\r\nChonburi 20110', 'Placing High Caliber Personnel\r\n\r\nBecause our focus is on the recruitment of high caliber Executives for our Client, our search and selection process has to be extraordinary thorough and deliberate. Our assignment handling process always starts with in-depth discussions with our Client concerning the required position\'s job description and requirements. The Client\'s company profile and related information should be provided to Pacific 2000 in order for us to truly &quot;know our Client&quot;.\r\n\r\nIn-depth interviews, together with some written tests if needed, are conducted after the Committee has chosen a number of Candidates to be interviewed. Only Candidates who have the qualifications to the preset requirements will be shortlisted to the Client.\r\n\r\nWe are seeking the sharpest � not the closest!\r\n\r\nTime-efficient way of finding &quot;The Right Person&quot;\r\n\r\nTime limitation is often a factor that obstructs the Company from getting personnel of the right caliber. A quality recruitment process is very time-consuming, especially when it involves media advertising. Pacific 2000 manages all the industry search through active headhunting and database screening. Our Client will then receive a shortlist of the most qualified Candidates within the agreed time schedule.\r\n\r\nA Perfect Match\r\n\r\nPacific 2000 ensures that the successful Candidate we place with the Company not only meets the requirements set forth by our Client, but also fits perfectly with the Company\'s corporate culture and environment. In addition, we assist both parties in the negotiation of a remuneration package that will benefit both sides.\r\n\r\nValue-added