(893, 'Microban (Asia) Ltd.', 0, NULL, NULL, 'pornthip@microban.co.th', '02-654-0909', '', '02-654-0903', 'M Thai Tower, 9th Fl., All Seasons Place, 87 Wireless Rd., Pathumwan, \r\nBangkok 10330', 'Microban International, Ltd.\r\nGlobal Headquarters\r\n11400 Vanstory Drive\r\nHuntersville, NC 28078\r\nUnited States\r\nPh: +1 (704) 875-0806', '', 'Microban International Ltd. is the global leader in built-in antimicrobial product protection, engineering durable antimicrobial solutions for consumer, industrial and medical products around the world. Microban protection can be engineered into a breadth of materials including: polymers, textiles, coatings, paper and adhesives.\r\n\r\nBuilt into products during the manufacturing process, Microban protection inhibits the growth of microbes. Microorganisms such as bacteria, mould and mildew can cause stains, odours and product deterioration. With Microban antimicrobial protection, microbial reproduction is inhibited throughout the product&rsquo;s useful lifetime. Microban\'s antimicrobial protection ensures continuous, durable and effective antimicrobial protection that provides an added level of defence against damaging microbes without ever wearing off or washing away.\r\n\r\nFounded in 1994 by three biomedical engineers, Microban International Ltd. is a wholly-owned subsidiary of Barr Brands International. Innovative Microban protection is built-in to over 1,000 products in more than 30 countries. With more than 250 clients, we are proud to supply our antimicrobial protection to customers with eight global offices spanning four continents. We&rsquo;re close to our customers, where they&rsquo;re headquartered, where they manufacture and where they sell. Check out our news, blogs and more to learn how Microban protection can keep your products cleaner and fresher.\r\n\r\nPhilip Visit and give Brochure  22/6/07\r\n\r\nCall   No new expat   12/1/07', '21', '1', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-19 10:49:28', '77', '24', '