(896, 'LEK Consulting Asia Pacific LLP', 0, NULL, NULL, 'a.chalat@lek.com', '02-654-3500', '', '02-654-3510', 'Suite 26/F Capital Towers All Seasons Place \n87/1 Wireless Road\nLumpini, Pathumwan\nBangkok 10330 Thailand', '', '', 'L.E.K.&rsquo;s Bangkok office has served as our Southeast Asia headquarters since the office opened in 1998. The team includes a group of Thai professionals working alongside consultants from the U.S. and other ASEAN countries; together they offer a powerful set of skills, experience and language capabilities required to serve our clients&rsquo; needs in Thailand and across the region.  Our unique combination of rigorous analytics, deep industry and market expertise, and strategic advisory capabilities provides our clients with the insights they need to make key decisions for their business.\r\n\r\nOur Specialties\r\n\r\nWe work with clients ranging from large and mid-sized corporations to financial investors and public sector entities.  Our work focuses on supporting clients in a number of ways to help them achieve their business goals, including:\r\n\r\nProviding strategic market insight for existing or new markets\r\nDeveloping successful and actionable growth strategies\r\nTurning around/improving business performance\r\nOptimizing business portfolio performance\r\nEvaluating and providing due diligence on potential investments\r\nStrategy activation\r\nWhile we work across numerous industry sectors, we bring particularly deep experience and expertise in the following industries:\r\n\r\nAviation &amp; Travel\r\nBiopharma &amp; Life Sciences\r\nBuilding Materials &amp; Industrial Products\r\nConsumer Products\r\nEnergy (O&amp;G, coal, power, renewables)\r\nHealthcare Services\r\nPrivate Equity\r\nRetail\r\nSurface Transport &amp; Logistics\r\nSee our case examples to learn more about how we work with our clients in Southeast Asia.\r\n\r\n- See more at: \r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Jan. 20, 2010 - Follow up by email. Jovelyn visited office: Jan. 19,