(903, 'The Boston Consulting Group Thailand Ltd', 0, NULL, NULL, 'oranwat.kingchat@bcg.com', '+66 2 667 3000 ', '', '02-667-3123', '37th Floor, U Chu Liang Bldg\r\n968 Rama lV Rd., Silom, Bangkok 10500', '', '', 'The Boston Consulting Group (BCG) was founded more than 40 years ago and is now one of the largest international management consulting firms.\r\n\r\nBCG undertakes assignments for major Thai and multinational companies in the areas of strategy formulation, business process engineering, market entry strategies, organizational development and product development strategies. \r\n\r\nBCG is well known for its development of management concepts which have profoundly changed the way most companies now think about themselves and their competition. These concepts include experience curve theory, time-based management and portfolio management matrix.\r\n\r\nBoston Consulting Group operates through 71 offices in 41 countries staffed with over 4,400 professionals. BCG became the first strategy consulting firm in Asia when it opened its Tokyo office in 1966. Presently, there are thirteen offices in Asia.\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Philip Visit and give Brochure 16/7/07 Interested Send E-mail Book 8/1/07&lt;/p&gt;', '7', '41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-19 11:43:53', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'www.bcg.com', '0', '5', '0', 5, '', NULL, '1', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
