(924, 'Magotteaux Co Ltd', 0, NULL, NULL, 'jarintip.udomchairassamee@mahotteaux.com', '02-210-0566-70', '', '02-210-0571', 'Room 312-3, 31st Fl., \r\n889 Thai CC Tower, \r\nSouth. Sathorn Rd., \r\nYannawa, Bangkok 10120', 'Rue A. Dumont\r\n4051 Vaux-sous-Ch&egrave;vremont\r\nBelgium', '', 'The Belgian foundry started in 1918 is now the world leader in differentiated solutions against wear. Magotteaux supplies the widest range of optimized solutions (products, services and systems) to industries involved in comminution (material size reduction): mines, cement, coal power stations, quarries and recycling. Magotteaux also designs specific solutions for the dredging industry.\r\n\r\nTo answer their customers&rsquo; needs, Magotteaux researches, designs, manufactures and distributes grinding media and wear resistant parts thanks to a thorough understanding of:\r\n- the production processes of the different customers,\r\n- the wear mechanisms (abrasion, corrosion,  impact) involved,\r\n- the material (alloy) aspects.\r\n\r\nOur services cover pre-sales (audits, analyses, diagnoses,&hellip;), sales (inc. installation, supervision and equipment fine-tuning) and after-sales (performance follow-up, real time mill management,&hellip;).', '2', '4', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-19 15:24:44', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.magotteaux.com/', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
