(1000, 'PepsiCo Services Asia Limited', 231, NULL, NULL, 'sureeporn.tirachot@intl.pepsico.com', '02-689-4600 Ext 4611', '', '02 664-7260', 'Emporium Building 17th Fl.\n622 Soi Sukhumvit Sukhumvit  Rd., \nKlongtoey, Klongtoey, \nBangkok 10110 Thailand', '', '', 'PepsiCo Services Asia Limited is an affiliated company of PepsiCo Inc. and has operated its business in the Foods and Beverages sector in Thailand. The company was founded in 1982 starting on beverage business, and then expanded to foods business in 1995, contributed to local jobs creating and providing technical supports and market opportunity for Thai potato farmers. \r\n\r\nThe beverage brands available in the Thai market are Pepsi Cola, Pepsi Max, Mirinda, 7-Up, Gatorade, Twister, and Lipton tea. For foods, the company produces, distributes, and markets a variety of salty or sweet, convenient, snacks under the brands of Lay&rsquo;s, Cheetos, Doritos, Twisties, Tawan, Stax, and Sunbite. In addition to snacks, the company has committed to continue providing more food and beverage choices made with wholesome ingredients that contribute to healthier eating and drinking, such as Quaker Oates. \r\n\r\nBesides the efforts on product development to improve consumers&rsquo; health and wellbeing, the company is fully committed to protecting the earth\'s natural resources through innovation and the efficient use of land, energy, water and packaging in all our operations, in order to deliver sustainable growth while investing in a healthier future.\r\n \r\n&lt;p&gt;K. Leslie Baldwin baldwin.leslie@gmail.com House #25 Soi Sukhumvit 43 17 Floor Philip and K.Nita Visit and give Cake 18/5/07 Philip Visit and give Brochure+Book 17/5/07 K.Banchaphon Srivanasont Executive Assistant E-mail :benchaphon.srivanasont@intl.pepsico.com K.Ping K.Pog (Hr) Gift Cookie 20/12/06&lt;/p&gt;', '52', '5', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-21 15:02:26', '77', '24', '2013-01-15', 'www.pepsithai.com', '0', '15', '0', 15, '', NULL, '7', ''