(1013, 'Standard Chartered Bank Thai PCL', 0, NULL, NULL, '', ' 02 724 4000 Ext 48704', '', '02-724-8008, 02-636-7130', '4th and 13th Floor , Sathorn Nakorn Tower \n90  North Sathorn Road Silom \nBangrak Bangkok 10500', '', '', 'Standard Chartered Bank has been in Thailand since 1894. In 1999 the Bank acquired a majority stake in Nakornthon Bank, which was then renamed Standard Chartered Nakornthon Bank. In 2005, the 2 banking operations were officially combined into a single entity called Standard Chartered Bank (Thai). \r\nStandard Chartered Bank (Thai) is a member of the Standard Chartered Group, a leading international bank. With 1,700 offices in 70 markets, Standard Chartered offers exciting and challenging international career opportunities for more than 87,000 staff. The Bank aspires to be the world&rsquo;s best international bank leading the way in Asia, Africa and the Middle East. Standard Chartered Bank in Thailand operates through 27 branches and has two core businesses:\r\n&bull; Consumer banking, which comprises consumer lending (unsecured and secured), consumer transaction banking, wealth management, priority banking, and SME banking.	\r\n&bull; Wholesale banking, which serves corporate and institutional clients with services in trade finance; cash management; lending; securities services; foreign exchange; debt capital marketing, etc.\r\n \r\n&lt;p&gt;April 29, 2011. K. Naruemon said that they are using Crown relocation as global agency. Crown relocation has global agreement to Standard Chartered. Visit and gift brochure 19/1/07 They have crown agant take care&lt;/p&gt;', '5', '4', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-21 16:37:51', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'www.standardchartered.co.th', '0', '20', '0', 20, '', NULL, '1', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(1014, 'The Swatch Group Trading Thailand Limited', 212, NULL, NULL, 'sgrth.reception@th.swatchgroup.com', '02-610-0216-7', '+662 610 02 00', '02-654-3246', '4th Floor, M. Thai Tower, All Seasons Place\n87 Wireless Road\nPathumwan District\nBangkok 10330', 'The Swatch Group Ltd\r\nSeevorstadt 6\r\n2501 Biel / Bienne\r\nSwitzerland', '', 'Swatch Group is an international group active in the design, manufacture and sale of finished watches, jewelry, watch movements and components.\r\n\r\nSwatch Group supplies nearly all components required by its 18 watch brands, and Swatch Group companies supply movements and components to third-party watchmakers in Switzerland and around the world. Please be sure to visit our brands\' websites to learn more about their fantastic products.\r\n\r\nSwatch Group is also a key player in the manufacture and sale of electronic systems used in watchmaking and other industries.\r\n\r\nSwatch Group employs more than 29 700 persons in over 50 countries. Gross sales in 2012 amounted to 8.143 billion Swiss francs (2011: 7.143), net profit to 1.608 billion Swiss francs (2011: 1.276 billion).\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Philip Visit and give Brochure 21/6/07 Call 12/1/07 K.Tangkwa () &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:sgrth.reception@th.swatchgroup.com&quot;&gt;sgrth.reception@th.swatchgroup.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: xx-small;&quot;&gt;Last Updte 08/01/2009 09:53:05 by lift &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nK. Siripen   Mahawattanangkul\r\nHuman Resource Manager\r\nsiripen.mahawattanangkul@th.swatchgroup.com\r\nsiripen.mahawattanangkul@th.swatchgroup.com', '12', '1', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-21 16:57:32', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.swatchgroup.com/en/', '0', '1', '0', 1, '', NULL, '2', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
