(1100, 'Bara Windsor amp Co Ltd', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info@barawindsor.com', '02 637 5000', '', '02 637 5039', 'U Chu Liang Building 968 \nRama IV Rd., Silom, Bangrak,\nBangkok 10500', '', 'Bara, Windsor &amp; Co., Ltd. \r\n\r\n', '   Established in 1953, Bara Windsor &amp; Co., Ltd. has successfully grown into a world class trading and manufacturing company with an international supplier and distribution net work. While much has changed, One thing has not : Our priorities on product innovation, business development, productivity enhancement, human resource development, Technical upgrading and so on through modernization and globalization of the management.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n           Our original philosophyHonesty, Integrity and Fairness, also remains the same...but it has been enhanced through the modern concept of  Management by Objectives  (MBO) , Which has helped put all our division and affiliates at the forefront of their respective industries.\r\n\r\n           We also continue to carry on the goodwill traditions of our founder, Mr.U Cha Liang, who believed that besides being responsible to our customers, shareholders suppliers and staffs, we must also contribute to the society through philanthropy and community service.\r\n\r\n            We at Bara, Windsor Co.,Ltd. Look forward to the years ahead. They hold many opportunities for us, and we are intent on maintaining our position as one of Thailand\'s business leaders.\r\n\r\nNo Foreigner Update \r\nCalled and they have their own hotel for their expat. Not interested in our service. so no need to update.', '39', '41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2016-05-27 13:49:38', '177', '24', '2014-01-15', 'http://www.barawindsor.com', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(1101, 'Khronos Advisory Limited', 0, NULL, NULL, 'paulc@khronosadivisory.com', '02 664 9100', '', '02 664 9110', '25/F (2-4) 622 Emporium Tower\nSukhumvit Road, Klongton\nKlongtoey\nBangkok 10110', '', '', 'Following the successful June 2009 acquisition of the advisory business of Imprimis Capital Management Limited in Southeast Asia, Khronos Advisory Limited commenced operations, continuing to provide financial and commercial advice to government clients and multinational corporations in the areas of mergers and acquisitions, joint-ventures, structured finance, capital raising, and liability restructuring.\r\nFor two decades, members of our team have worked in Southeast Asia and have developed proven skills and experience in corporate finance advisory, mergers and acquisitions, and project development. As Khronos, we aim to deliver client service that ranks us amongst the top bespoke advisers in the region.\r\n\r\nKhronos Advisory excels in advising clients over the entire course of the deal process, from conception through to execution. We pride ourselves on our client, rather than transaction, focus. Clients can expect proactive, individualized and discreet advice with specialized insights and knowledge in our key sectors.\r\n\r\nKhronos Advisory Limited is a member of several organizations including:\r\nClass A qualified financial adviser, Ministry of Finance, Thailand; \r\nJuristic Member of the Thai Institute of Directors Association; \r\nMember of The Australian-Thai Chamber of Commerce; \r\nMember of The Thai Chamber of Commerce.', '5', '5', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-22 16:53:04', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'www.khronosadvisory.com', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
