(1123, 'PQ Chemicals Thailand Limited', 0, NULL, NULL, 'vikromw@pqthai.com', '02-229-4694', '', '02-229-4689', 'Times Square Building 26th Floor.,Room #02\n246 Sukhumvit Road\nKlongtoey \nBangkok 10110', '', '', 'PQ Chemicals (Thailand) Limited or PQCT manufactures, sells, exports and distributes zeolite, Valfor 100 for laundry detergent, and a range of specialty zeolites. PQCT is a wholly owned subsidiary of the PQ Corporation in Malvern, PA. Initially a 20,000 ton/a zeolite plant started production in 1993. This was expanded to 40,000 ton/a in 1995, and further to 60,000 ton/a in December 2005. \r\n\r\nThe PQ Corporation, one of the world\'s largest silicates producers, provided its latest technology and know-how for the plant. The locally produced zeolite permits detergent manufacturers to replace zeolite imports. It is also an environmentally friendly alternative for STPP or phosphates, in powder detergents. PQ Chemicals (Thailand) Limited exports zeolites as well to various countries in the region and further afield, as far as Latin America.', '56', '5', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-23 13:31:19', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'www.pqcorp.com', '0', '1', '0', 1, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(1124, 'Plexal Group Thailand Ltd', 0, NULL, NULL, 'dpaton@plexalgroup.com', '02-793-8900, dean mobile: 08 6526 2551', '', '02-793-8901', 'Rasa Tower I, 14th Floor, Unit 1401-1404 \n555 Phaholyothin Road \nChatuchak\nBangkok 10900', '', '', 'Plexal Group is an independent company with a core group of people who have specialist expertise, backed by many years in the field.\r\n\r\nOur people have the expertise and experience to provide engineering services across the following focus areas:\r\nMulti-discipline engineering\r\nTurnkey Control &amp; Safeguarding Systems\r\nTurnkey Historian / PIMS\r\nTurnkey Metering\r\nMulti-discipline commissioning\r\nLifecycle inspections including Hazardous Area &amp; SIL\r\n\r\nWe have comprehensive knowledge across Upstream Oil &amp; Gas, LNG, Gas Transmission, CSG, Water Utilities and Power Generation. We also support Mining, Mineral Processing, Petrochemical, Alternative Energy and Waste Treatment.\r\n\r\nOur scope of supply includes:\r\nAssessments;\r\nConceptual;\r\nFront-end and detailed design;\r\nProcurement;\r\nSystem development and testing;\r\nFunctional Safety Lifecycle Services;\r\nConstruction management;\r\nCommissioning;\r\nTraining;\r\nDevelopment of Start-up / Shutdown procedures and Operations Manuals; and\r\nHandover to Operations.\r\nThis allows us to integrate various third-party technologies and develop specific solutions that optimise plant performance without significant changes to major equipment. We have developed efficiency tools (Plexsys&copy;, Plexispec&copy; and Pleximus&copy;) to help us better deliver projects for our clients.', '40', '3', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2013-11-23 13:28:12', '77', '2', '2014-01-15', 'www.plexalgroup.com', '0', '6', '0', 6, '', NULL, '1', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
