(1175, 'CIGNA Insurance Public Company Limited', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'executiveth@cigna.com', '02-651-5595 Ext 201', '', '02-650-9600', 'Q. House Ploenchit Building, 7th -10th Floor, \n598 Ploenchit Road, Lumpini, \nPathumwan, Bangkok, 10330', '', '', 'Cigna (NYSE:CI), an U.S.-based global health service company. Cigna Corporation&rsquo;s operating subsidiaries provide an integrated suite of medical, dental, behavioral health, pharmacy and vision care benefits, group and individual life, accident and disability insurance, to 70 million people around the world. \r\n\r\nCigna established a presence in Thailand in 2002 through Cigna International Marketing (Thailand) Limited. The Company has a strong in-house team of more than 800 telemarketers to promote health &amp; accident insurance products and services through telemarketing and direct response marketing channels. Cigna Insurance Public Company Limited, made its official debut in 2007, to play a significant role of an affinity-based telemarketing and multi distribution business specializing in Health and Personal Accident insurance products in Thailand.\r\n\r\nProducts or Services\r\n&bull;	Leader of Affinity - based telemarketing and direct marketing in Thailand\r\n&bull;	Innovator of Health and Personal Accident Insurance plans , Dental plan, Vision plan, etc. \r\n&bull;	Pioneer in offering direct to consumer products via direct response TV &amp; Global Health Benefits Plans in Thailand\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Update 9/11/06&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Katherine Aphaivongs&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sales Director&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;085 245 1100&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:Katherine.aphaivongs@cigna.com&quot;&gt;Katherine.aphaivongs@cigna.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '54', '1', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '2015-02-16 14:23:40', '153', '', '2014-01-15', 'www.cigna.co.th', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
