(1757, 'New International School of Thailand NIST', NULL, 35, NULL, 'ytrisynthia@nist.ac.th', '02 017 5888', '', '02253 1193', '36 Soi 15 Sukhumvit Road, \nKlong ton nua\nWattana Bangkok 10110', '', '', 'NIST is a Truly International School in the Heart of Bangkok  \r\n\r\nNIST International School (Bangkok, Thailand), is the most established accredited IB World School in the heart of Bangkok that offers all three International Baccalaureate (IB) programmes: Primary Years Programme (PYP), Middle Years Programme (MYP) and Diploma Programme (DP). \r\n\r\nLocated in Bangkok&rsquo;s foremost business, diplomatic, residential and shopping areas, the school sits on a well-appointed campus with state-of-the-art technology providing an international curriculum to a diverse group of students from over 50 nationalities ranging from 3 to 18 years of age. \r\n\r\nSince its inception in 1992, with guidance and support from the United Nations, NIST has gained a reputation as one of the leading IB schools in the world. Its students consistently earn high scores in the IB Diploma and move on to higher education in North America, Europe, and Australasia. Accredited by both the CIS and NEASC, NIST was the first school in Thailand to achieve dual accreditation.\r\n\r\nCurrently NIST teaches Thai, Japanese, Mandarin, Hindi, German, Korean and English as Mother Tongue Languages, as well as offering French, Mandarin, and Spanish as second languages. In addition to its world language programme, NIST has extensive extra-curricular activities from sports to clubs to instrumental music lessons. ', '35', '5', '2007-05-10 09:27:19', NULL, '2016-07-16 15:28:42', '177', '16', '2012-08-15', 'www.nist.ac.th', '0', '0', '1', 0, '', NULL, '12', '15000', '200000', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
