(1945, 'The Consulate  General of the Republic of Malta', 139, NULL, NULL, 'joy@wondervacation.com', '(+66) (2) 2349729 (+66) (2) 2336872', '', '(+66) (2) 2366538 (+66) (2) 2366540', 'Maltese Consulate in Bangkok, Thailand \r\n485/21 Narathivasrahanakarin Road, Silom Bangkok 10500 Thailand', '', '', 'The Malta Consulate in Bangkok is a satellite office of the Malta Embassy in the region, manned by fewer staff, and headed by a Malta national having the title Consul or Honorary Consul. The Malta consulate would usually be able to provide most of the consular services given by a Malta Embassy but on the spot, at a local level.\r\n \r\nConsulate Services could be consular assistance to Malta nationals who might be situated in or nearby Bangkok or to Thailand nationals who want to travel to Malta. Any problems involving Malta citizens over and above the scope of authority of the Malta Consulate in Bangkok can always be referred on to the Malta Embassy in Thailand itself. \r\n\r\nMalta Consulate Appointment - Many Consulates nowadays need visitors to make an appointment first before they visit the consulate. In most cases you are able to arrange an appointment by telephone or at the Consulate website. On the official website of the Malta Consulate in Bangkok you can find all the information on opening hours and appointments.\r\n\r\nConsulate in Bangkok:\r\nConsulate Hours: 09.00 - 15.00 \r\n \r\n ', '32', '8', '2007-05-10 16:04:00', NULL, '2013-11-25 10:02:53', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', '', '1', '0', '0', 4, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
