(2194, 'Gulf Agency Company Thailand Ltd', 0, NULL, NULL, 'thailand@gacworld.com', '02 650 7400, 02 650 7420', '', '02 650 7401', '9th Floor, Orakarn Building \r\n26/30-31 Ploenchit Rd. Lumpini, Pathumwan, Bangkok 10330', '', '', 'GAC has been operating in Thailand since 1992 and is part of the GAC group. The GAC Group is committed to ensuring customers&rsquo; needs for quality shipping, logistics and marine services are understood and met. And with over 10,000 professionals working around the clock, speaking more than 100 languages, at more than 300 offices in over 40 countries, we deliver that promise.\r\n\r\nThe GAC brand reflects quality, continuity, innovation and global reach. GAC in Thailand offers our customers a unique combination of Logistics and Shipping Agency Services. Our dedicated logistics team offer our customers a wide range of services including Ocean and Air freight, Warehousing and Distribution services sea freight and Customs Clearance. With more than 200 dedicated staff GAC strategically located offices in Bangkok , Amata Nakorn, Eastern Seaboard Industrial Estate, Bangpa In, Laem Chabang, Suvanabhumi Airport, Sattahip and Songkhla, we provide seamless services to all our customers.\r\n\r\nGAC Thailand is an ISO 9001:2008 certified company\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;American cham 11/05/07&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;transportation and logistics&lt;/p&gt;', '18', '0', '2007-05-11 12:10:57', NULL, '2013-11-23 14:37:56', '77', '24', '2014-01-15', 'www.gac.com', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', NULL, '0', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
